<br>
Farm IG's/HG's for cash, etc...  <br>
<br>
While HG's are easy enough.  Never really fought IG's.  <br>
<br>
What are the best pet/spell combos for fighting IG's at 60?  <br>
<br>
Also, anyone have any recommendations of where money would be easier?  Thanks in advance. <p><div align="center"> 
  <p><code>Vandalle Gott<br>
    52 Reaver of Innoruuk<br>
    Leader of Valiant Coalition<br>Saryrn</code></p>
  <p><i>"The final spark that blew life into me,
the DEMON OF THE FALL."</i></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xikbus>Xikbus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 60<br> <font color=#333333>(11/30/02 2:06:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=428.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: 60 Mage</span><hr size=1> Epic or no?  doesn't really matter all that much, but will change the speed a little bit.<br>
<br>
With epic, summon epic, and go to town on HGs.  I have always gotten better money with them then the IGs.  Just let the pet tank one or two at a time, and you will be set.<br>
<br>
Same without epic, just use 57 earth and chain cast when needed.  Will need to DS this pet.<br>
<br>
Don't forget to cast burnout on either pet while hunting too... <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104988">Xik</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=mantria>Mantria</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Mage</span><br>  Posts: 399<br> <font color=#333333>(12/10/02 8:52:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=428.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.DaveShirley.org/neil/rock_beast_03_t%5B1%5D.gif height=150 width=150></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: 60 Mage</span><hr size=1> hillgiants by far will be faster cash. they are alot lower level, die alot faster and there are tons more of those then the ones you can get in everfrost.  just setup on the plateau and kill to your hearts content.<br>
